# Math

## Base 7

+[Base 7](#base-7)

https://leetcode.com/problems/base-7/

```python
def convertToBase7(self, num: int) -> str:
        n = ''
        k = 1
        if num < 0:
            num = num * (-1)
            k = -1
        if num == 0:
            return '0'
        if num >0:
            while num != 0:
                n = n + str(num % 7)
                num = num // 7
            n = n[::-1]    
            return(str(int(n)*k))    
```
